Model: can you make a simple random forest classifier

Synthesize a neuro-symbolic classifier that utilizes a shallow Radial Basis Function (RBF) network to extract non-linear kernels, which are then fed into a symbolic rule-induction engine. The model must dynamically weight the influence of the symbolic rules based on the local density of the training data in the feature space, using a custom implementation of a Gaussian Mixture Model to determine that density
